          "fragmented",
          "concise",
          "dramatic",
          "instant"
        ],
        "hint": "natural: 自然停顿，像人说话 | fragmented: 短句连发，像聊天框 | concise: 尽量不分段 | dramatic: 长停顿，有情绪 | instant: 不分段"
